# gen84: hypothesis mode — "suppose X, then Y" creates a scoped fact
# and queries against it.
> suppose rex is a dog, then is rex a dog?
< Yes, under that supposition.
> suppose rex is a cat, then is rex a dog?
< No, even with that supposition.
# Supposition doesn't persist — rex is NOT known as a dog now.
> is rex a dog?
< I don't know about dog.
